00:21:49.434 --> 00:21:50.602 position:50% align:center
[LEON]
So you are Rimuru?

00:21:50.685 --> 00:21:52.896 position:50% align:center
[SHION]
Uh!

00:21:52.979 --> 00:21:54.814 position:50% align:center
