00:23:05.427 --> 00:23:06.928 position:50% align:center
Huh...? Mm?!

00:23:08.638 --> 00:23:10.056 position:50% align:center
[RIMURU]
Milim!

00:23:11.474 --> 00:23:15.020 position:50% align:center
[RIMURU] Oh, good.
